===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|abod}}, {{m|ang|abad}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ābād}}, first person past singular indicative of {{m|ang|ābīdan||to abide}}; see {{m|en|abide}}. Cognate with {{cog|sco|abade}}, {{m|sco|abaid||abode}}. For the change of nouns, compare {{m|en|abode|id=verb}}, preterite of {{m|en|abide}}.

